    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>(B) Some authors provided little information about their algorithms, which makes it difficult to re-implement the approaches.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="RU-RU" changeid="eugeneai" changedate="20161212T040456Z" creationid="eugeneai" creationdate="20161212T040456Z">
        <seg>-</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>(C) We speculated that minor variations in datasets, algorithms, or user populations inevitably lead to strong variations in the performance of the approaches.</seg>
      </tuv>
